            {
               "text": "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflection 3: Abstracting</b><br /><br />Has it ever crossed your mind that something that always surrounds us and makes life possible—like the atmosphere—can also be understood as an abstraction?</div></div></center>",
